  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA15">
<l>niṉaintiruntu vāṉavarka ṇīḷmalarāṟ pātam</l>
<l>puṉaintu maṭiporunta māṭṭār - niṉaintiruntu</l>
<l>miṉceyvāṉ ceñcaṭaiyāy vētiyaṉē yeṉkiṉṟēṟ</l>
<l>keṉceyvāṉ kollō viṉi</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Keeping thinking [of him] the celestials, although decorating [their] feet</l>
<l>with long blossoms could not join [his] feet. To me who, keeps thinking</l>
<l>[and] says “you with matted hair red so as to emit lightning, Veda expert”,</l>
<l>what will he do now?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
